text: "Eat It" is a song by "Weird Al" Yankovic. It is a parody of the song "Beat It" by Michael Jackson. It was released in 1984 for the album "Weird Al" Yankovic in 3-D. A music video was made for the song that is a direct parody of the "Beat It" video. Category:"Weird Al" Yankovic songs Category:Parodies Category:1984 songs
title: Eat It
